{"tid":2290352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港共佔時期，又稱為香港共治時期或香港淪陷時期","createTime":"2020-11-18T03:00:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T03:41:57.000Z","uid":137897,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1fe74578172042d61367d56c0f4766ba68bc8c53","tid":2290352,"uid":137897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:00:11.000Z","msg":"香港共佔時期，又稱為香港共治時期或香港淪陷時期，是指2019年初夏「反對逃犯條例運動」後共匪占領香港的時期，香港人俗稱這段時期為「三年零八個月」。"},{"pid":"6bf329ce31528e80d9c67371de64b16c58ba329d","tid":2290352,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:03:04.000Z","msg":"吓<br />\n唔係97後起計？<br />\n低能"},{"pid":"37f3878b7b69de1b95ea36d744e25868da26b671","tid":2290352,"uid":137897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/18zXxB7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F18zXxB7.jpg&h=a8efce25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uMsaSCn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuMsaSCn.jpg&h=730032d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年6月12日共匪佔領金鐘一刻"},{"pid":"63b33857d6b5d410ec9044580c89505e0f679a11","tid":2290352,"uid":137897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e9wrqYn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe9wrqYn.jpg&h=29ab9a10&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LZXFvp4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLZXFvp4.jpg&h=03de1780&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當時正在保衞香港的平民"},{"pid":"a5336e151e28db9fc8951748c70c5b1a0176f1b8","tid":2290352,"uid":137897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:13:47.000Z","msg":"共匪軍佔領香港後隨即成立國安署，由燉餅強出任最高長官，自共匪入侵香港以來，共匪便在香港虐待平民和義士，又推行国民教育，除了禁止使用廣東話及強迫使用匪語外，在香港島及九龍的主要街道與地區名稱，亦被佔領地政府更換為共式地名，例如皇后大道中被改成「總書記大道中」。"},{"pid":"5a4a6964d4b2d564855b0c8e800fe29d8ab89373","tid":2290352,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:15:46.000Z","msg":"死五毛，97已經有解放軍啦"},{"pid":"0cf125107b31ba29aed5e0bb23b69683def40703","tid":2290352,"uid":266342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:41:57.000Z","msg":"係「支佔」"}]}